{
  "id": "adv_group_tri_05_05",
  "title": "TRINITYAiLE 05 05",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、私、行くね\n見送りありがとう、瑠依ちゃん、優ちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm going now.\nThanks for seeing me off‚ Rui-chan‚ Yu-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 6.863990879,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 7.0773241361
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "……なぁ、すみれちゃん\nやっぱり、うちらも一緒に――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hey‚ Sumire-chan.\nMaybe we should still go with you――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.0773241361,
      "endTime": 11.4076414426,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 11.6076414426
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "ううん、二人は来ちゃダメだよ\nだって、ファンのみんなが待ってるんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ you two can't come.\nBecause our fans are waiting for us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.6076414426,
      "endTime": 17.8933114269,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 18.0999770165
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……それは、あなただって同じでしょ、すみれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But that applies to you too‚ Sumire.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.0999770165,
      "endTime": 22.566666666699998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "ファンは三人のTRINITYAiLEを観たいのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Our fans want to see the three of us as TRINITYAiLE.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.9,
      "endTime": 25.853809452100002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 26.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "……瑠依ちゃん、そのことはもう\nいっぱい話し合ったよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Rui-chan‚ we've already\ntalked about that a lot‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.0666666667,
      "endTime": 30.817278639599998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 31
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "私は、もう私のために誰にも夢を\n諦めてほしくないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't want anyone to give up their dreams\nfor my sake anymore.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31,
      "endTime": 36.8915641626,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 37.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "このまま中途半端に続けてたら\n絶対に、二人の夢を邪魔することになる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I continue half-heartedly like this‚\nI'll definitely end up hindering your dreams.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.1,
      "endTime": 43.1365687787,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "……結局、私はこうなっちゃったけど\n瑠依ちゃんと優ちゃんなら、きっと二人でも大丈夫",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…In the end‚ this is what happened to me‚\nbut Rui-chan and Yu-chan‚ you'll be fine even with just the two of you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.0333333333,
      "endTime": 51.928682823900004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 53.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "私が、いなくても、二人なら、きっと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even without me‚ you two will surely…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.3,
      "endTime": 59.0121313095,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 59.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "すみれちゃん……そんな悲しいこと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire-chan… Don't say such sad things…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.2333333333,
      "endTime": 63.333333285600006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "私も待ってるわ。すみれが帰ってくるのを\nいつまでも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll be waiting too. For you to come back‚ Sumire.\nAlways.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.5333333333,
      "endTime": 68.4208380858,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 68.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "だから、お願い。すみれも夢を諦めないで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So please‚ don't give up on your dream‚ Sumire.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.7666666667,
      "endTime": 72.3459184806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 72.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "そうやで、すみれちゃん。うちも、ずっと待ってるから\n……いつ帰って来てもええように",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right‚ Sumire-chan. I'll be waiting too.\n…So that you can come back anytime.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.5333333333,
      "endTime": 79.45777713470001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "……ごめんなさい、今までいっぱい迷惑掛けたのに\n最後、こんな風になって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I'm sorry‚ I've caused you so much trouble‚\nand now‚ at the end‚ it's come to this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.9333333333,
      "endTime": 88.37946787409999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 88.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "でも、二人に会えて本当に良かった\nトリエルで歌えたことは、私にとって一生の宝物だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I'm truly glad I met you two.\nSinging as TRINITYAiLE will always be a treasure to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.5666666667,
      "endTime": 97.76498815219999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 98.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "今まで、ありがとう、私のお姉ちゃん達\nさよなら、元気でね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for everything‚ my dear sisters.\nGoodbye‚ take care!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.7666666667,
      "endTime": 105.5433511916,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 106.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "うちは……うちは絶対、絶対、さよならなんて\n言わへんからな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I… I'll never‚ ever\nsay goodbye…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.5666666667,
      "endTime": 114.8064397018,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 115
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "……こんな終わり方、私は嫌\nでも、優……私達これからどうすれば……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I hate this ending.\nBut Yu… what should we do now…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115,
      "endTime": 123.52643956050001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 123.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "……正直、うちもまだ考えがまとまってないわ\nけど、何もしないって選択肢だけは、なしやな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Honestly‚ I haven't figured it out yet either.\nBut doing nothing is not an option.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.7,
      "endTime": 132.7280041853,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 132.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "このままだと、すみれは本当に芸能界を引退してしまう\n……勝手だと分かってるけど……私は、絶対に嫌",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we leave it like this‚ Sumire will really retire from the entertainment industry.\n…I know it's selfish of me… but I absolutely hate that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.9,
      "endTime": 142.33333333329998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 138.2
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 142.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "そんなん、うちだって同じ気持ちや\nすみれちゃんの明るさに、ずっと助けられてきたからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I feel the same way.\nHer cheerfulness has always helped me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.6333333333,
      "endTime": 150.0144437873,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 145.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 150.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_05-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "私達だけじゃない、ファンだってそうよ\nすみれは絶対にトリエルに必要なメンバーなの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not just us‚ the fans too.\nSumire is definitely a necessary member of TRINITYAiLE.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.2,
      "endTime": 157.3842847301,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
